For running metax please run:
	1. $ npm install
	2. npm start storage=[storage_path] port=[port_number] key=[ssl_private_key_path] cert=[ssl_certificate_path]
	example:
		$ npm start storage=./storage/ port=8001 key=./keys/privkey.pem cert=./keys/fullchain.pem

For running test please run:
	$ npm run test
